
::SAGA DOCUMENTATION FILE::

:ADAPTOR NAME:

  HDFS Adaptor
  
:AUTHORS:

  Copyright (c) 2009 Chris Miceli <cmicel1@cct.lsu.edu>

:LICENSE:

  Distributed under the Boost Software License, Version 1.0.

:ADAPTOR LIBRARY NAME:
  
  libsaga_adaptor_hdfs_file.so (dylib)

:IMPLEMENTS PACKAGE:
 
  - saga_package_file
  - saga_package_namespace

:DESCRIPTION:

 The HDFS file adaptor allos file access that are stored on a 
 Hadoop Distributed File System.

:URL SCHEMES:

  - hdfs://

:REQUIRES:

  The HDFS file adaptor requires the Java Runtime Environment (JRE) and
  the libhdfs (http://wiki.apache.org/hadoop/LibHDFS) library that is
  included but not built in a default HDFS installation.


:CONFIGURE OPTIONS:

  | --with-java=DIR   use java (default is YES) at DIR (optional) |\\
  |                                                               |\\
  | JAVA_LOCATION     JAVA installation root (JAVA_HOME)          |\\
  
:KNOWN ISSUES:

  See https://macpro01.cct.lsu.edu/trac/saga/query?status=assigned&status=new&status=reopened&component=HDFS+Adaptor&order=priority
